      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already tried doing that thing where you swallow or blow your nose to pop it back and nothing happened. it's just a ringing sound and stuck feeling. i really don't want to deal with a hospital at 11pm if it's just a clogged ear canal. are you sure it's not just a bit of wax or something? can i just try some ear drops or wait until tomorrow morning to see if it clears up?",
